# Phase 24 quality-gate outputs (Plan 05)
# .lighthouseci/ is created by `npx lhci autorun` at phase close (plan 07)
# and contains JSON reports + LHR HTML — large + machine-generated.
# visual-check PNGs are produced by tests/e2e/v13-visual-capture.spec.ts
# (36 fullPage PNGs per run); .gitkeep preserves the directory while the
# PNGs themselves stay out of history. Operators who want to commit
# visual evidence can `git add -f <path>` selectively.
.lighthouseci/
.planning/phases/*/visual-check/*.png

/.tmp-verify
